title: Team Brunel edge AkzoNobel by less than five minutes to win Leg 9 of Volvo Ocean Race
text:
Team Brunel edge AkzoNobel by less than five minutes to win Leg 9 of Volvo Ocean Race 10:22am BST - 01:23
Team Brunel wins Leg 9 of the Volvo Ocean Race by just over four minutes from AkzoNobel to close the gap on overall leaders DongFeng ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
